            "answer": "<p>No. Rejuvia uses a low 2mg dose of melatonin — most gummies pack 5-10mg — paired with natural sleep herbs that calm your mind without knocking you out. You get deep, restorative sleep and wake up clear-headed, not hungover.</p>"
